With Tinder, we built Ex-orcise — where closure came with a punching bag.
And Ex-presso Run, a 2Km sprint that ended in a coffee rave, because healing tastes better with caffeine and dance.

From punching bags to coffee raves, we helped make moving on the new glow-up.
